            <p class="par-lg">Apart from the university, the University Heights real estate also enjoys close proximity to the Foothills Medical Centre, the McMahon Stadium, the Foothills Athletic Park and the Childrenâ€™s Hospital. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The fact that the community lies in a posh and active neighborhood, renders the average asking-price for real estate above the Calgary real estate average.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">There are a variety of public and private Schools in University Heights including Banff Trail, University Heights Elementary School, Branton, William Aberhart, Queen Elizabeth Junior High School, Senator Patrick Burns and many more.</p>
